                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:start&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-style:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-ligatures:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration-thickness:initial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration-style:initial&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration-color:initial&quot;&gt;Hi &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;{{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Your provider recommended to donate blood, as discussed during your lab review. Please note that this request is separate from the initial blood draw you had to produce lab results.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You may donate at the American Red Cross (download their app and schedule), or you may go to a local facility of your choice that offers &amp;ldquo;therapeutic phlebotomy&amp;rdquo;.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Attached is a copy of your signed&lt;strong&gt; 10X Health Therapeutic Phlebotomy Order&lt;/strong&gt; and&lt;strong&gt; 10X Health Blood Donation Approval Form&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
You may provide a printed copy of the &lt;strong&gt;10X Health Therapeutic Phlebotomy&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Order &lt;/strong&gt;to a diagnostic center near you to authorize the procedure. The &lt;strong&gt;10X Health Blood Donation Approval Form&lt;/strong&gt; must be filled out before leaving the diagnostic center and then sent to our 10X Health team for approval. Please read below the detailed instructions.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: start; margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;1. You will need to print and provide a copy of the&lt;strong&gt; 10X Health Therapeutic Phlebotomy Order &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;and&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt; 10X Health Blood Donation Approval Form &lt;/strong&gt;(both attached to this email) to the diagnostic center at the time of your blood draw.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:start&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: start; margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;2. Once your blood draw has been completed, you will receive confirmation from the diagnostician of a successful donation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:start&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: start; margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;3. Before leaving, you must fill out the &lt;strong&gt;10X Health Blood Donation Approval Form&lt;/strong&gt; and you must take a picture of your &lt;strong&gt;Single Donation Record (SDR)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:start&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: start; margin-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;4. Reply to this email and forward the filled out &lt;strong&gt;10X Health Blood Donation Approval Form&lt;/strong&gt; and a picture of your &lt;strong&gt;Single Donation Record (SDR)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:start&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;Once your information has been reviewed and approved, your wellness advisor will contact you regarding ordering.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
We&amp;#39;re excited to be taking this journey with you and always happy to help! Please don&amp;#39;t hesitate to reach out with any questions or concerns.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
To your wellness,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;10&lt;span style=&quot;color:#cc0000;&quot;&gt;X&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Health System&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;
Main: 305.682.1818&lt;br aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;
Fax: 786.598.8612&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://10xhealthsystem.com&quot;&gt;10xhealthsystem.com&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</value>
